title: WESTWORLD SEASON 4 Theories & Season 3's Unanswered Questions Explained!
author: Think Story
comment: Thanks for sticking with me through all these videos! I had a blast making them. I hope you'll subscribe as I take on new shows and films :)
This season made me feel like I watched so much and nothing at the same time.
I really missed Anthony Hopkins this season!
9:29: Maybe there will be a GoT park, so in future seasons we'll get to see a proper ending for GoT, being played out inside the Westworld universe.

Bernard could always remake Delores the same way Delores made Bernard based on her memories of Arnold. As long as someone remembers you, you never really die. EDIT: got to the end of the video see that you mentioned this.
description:
